name: OCBeachScanner
0:
”Alexa, open o. c. beach scanner”
”Alexa, start o. c. beach scanner”
”Alexa, play o. c. beach scanner”
skdetail:
Rated: Guidance Suggested. This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: o. c. beach scanner
des: OC BeachScanner is the app that allows you to listen into the Ocean City Maryland Fire and Police action live. This audio includes Worcester County Fire, Highway and MD State Police. Just say "Hey Alexa, Start OC BeachScanner!"
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
